{"tid":2102722,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日做咩好","createTime":"2020-07-10T16:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T20:23:47.000Z","uid":48443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4b17944bcc1a54cf9cef0ea514958a796f2443b6","tid":2102722,"uid":48443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:21:10.000Z","msg":"只做一件事<br />\n就係投票 投票 投票"},{"pid":"6913482c5b2681cff690a2a4ddf7be0c944920a3","tid":2102722,"uid":44815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:23:08.000Z","msg":"投票投票齊投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3e30ea8473894072274335095dde9964e02b5e","tid":2102722,"uid":21486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A1zBrdj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA1zBrdj.png&h=dc3b6e2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n順便幫手 Share：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkfactcheck.io/posts/318029346266274\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fposts%2F318029346266274&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumqjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=d3b23876\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkfactcheck.io/posts/318029346266274</a>"},{"pid":"de4274c3f418f1f8f4a87783822959860ca22c60","tid":2102722,"uid":350524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:41:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2f9b2a51083dd2a43065c74e3b054c1de187fa0b","tid":2102722,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b17944bcc1a54cf9cef0ea514958a796f2443b6","tid":2102722,"uid":48443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:21:10.000Z","msg":"只做一件事<br />\n就係投票 投票 投票"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T20:23:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PowerForDemocracy/photos/a.808713395853924/3191030574288849/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPowerForDemocracy%2Fphotos%2Fa.808713395853924%2F3191030574288849%2F&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumqjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=2912172e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PowerForDemocracy/photos/a.808713395853924/3191030574288849/</a><br />\n<br />\n【民主派35+公民投票 (初選)】#重要訊息 #請廣傳 : #服務站開放時間須延後至中午十二時！<br />\n<br />\n警方於7月10日晚，突進入 #香港民意研究所 對其電腦系統進行調查，導致#民主派初選 的最後階段準備工作被延誤。<br />\n<br />\n在此重申，初選所使用的是另一獨立電腦系統，警方的調查並不會影響於7月11日至7月12日進行的民主派初選。<br />\n<br />\n#民主動力 及兩位初選協調人獲悉香港民意研究所團隊的工作日程被打亂，亦以防萬一，<span class=\"gold\">技術團隊因系統安全考慮，正為系統重設加密匙。因此，#7月11日所有服務站的開放時間須延後至中午十二時正，敬請留意！</span><br />\n<br />\n同時，<span class=\"red\">Android 使用者將不能使用手機應用程式投票，投票方式將採用投票網頁進行投票。而IOS使用者則不受影響，依舊採用投票網頁進行投票。</span><br />\n<br />\n因此做成的不便，我們謹向廣大市民致歉。望所有投票的市民，能多多包容及忍耐。<br />\n<br />\n在惡法橫行的時代，我們要繼續不畏強權，以公民投票去拒絕謊言。提提大家，投票時除展示身份證外，須攜帶：✅過往的投票通知書 或 ✅住址證明 (文本、電子版本、截圖及相片皆接納)。<br />\n<br />\n#民主派 #35plus #公民投票 #初選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"right\">[重要！] 聽日7月11號  12點先開票站<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2102850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2102850</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</p>"}]}